{"tid":546651,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"暗戀既男仔辭職了","createTime":"2018-01-31T17:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T15:39:32.000Z","uid":56544,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8472fcadd80370dd1bc3383861049248947be6","tid":546651,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"有啲1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個男仔係我返pt識既<br />\n我同佢只係同事 一啲都唔熟 只會因為公事而講兩句<br />\n佢係一個好慢熱既男仔 我嘗試過打開話題 但佢覆左兩句都已經已讀不回左我<br />\n我都知我毒 唔識開話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一早知道佢會resign 佢最近真係resign左啦 我望住佢走既背影 我勁多野想同佢講 我想同佢講 我暗戀左佢好耐 但我冇咁做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係懦弱既垃圾 我只可以係連登祝你以後既日子都過得開心同完成到你既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390047a6f786b7da7685f52de4a10d5b4a0ef359","tid":546651,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cc4de9f1b8529122f38eba52f27cf3b481b23a6","tid":546651,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e5233156c5ae5b1d32ad481b253682d65f90ba3","tid":546651,"uid":56544,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"9cc4de9f1b8529122f38eba52f27cf3b481b23a6","tid":546651,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"正常掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nkeep住有男仔追下咁"},{"pid":"c95e72d7cc78ab5b1b0b025e2f91f9cf9e2f9ce1","tid":546651,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390047a6f786b7da7685f52de4a10d5b4a0ef359","tid":546651,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score